  "text": "Such setups can even be used to perform tomographic bio-imaging [CITATION_1] . Another major potential application of this technique is spectroscopy, since samples may be probed in frequency domains which are different from where detection is performed [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
